title: Plat mid main LF a Jungle or ADC duo to push to Diamond with.
body:
Hi. I'm LF a Plat+ jungler main with a WR of over 55% to duo with. I usually one trick anivia. 

Profile:
http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=An%20itchy%20scrotum

http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=herbsss

I usually float between 60-70% W/R. Never really played many games during the season, but would like to push to Diamond with a good jungler. Add the first account if you'd like to duo.
